name: Natural Daily Moisturizer 1.7oz
description: A nutrient-rich moisturizer that blankets the skin with an all-day ready, feather light layer of hydration. Light and comfortable formula suitable for all skin types. Ingredients: Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Glycerin, Musa Sapientum (Banana) Fruit Extract, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Stearic acid, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Cetostearyl Alcohol, Polysorbate 60, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter
